    <item>
      <title>马克龙称选举结果旨在避免秋季出现混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/macron-says-election-decision-aimed-to-avoid-disarray-in-autumn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙再次试图解释其解散议会的决定，称他的目的是考虑到其政党在欧洲选举中遭遇的失败，并避免未来出现更大的动荡风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/macron-says-election-decision-aimed-to-avoid-disarray-in-autumn</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 19:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯达吉斯坦六名警察和一名牧师被杀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/six-police-officers-and-a-priest-killed-in-russia-s-dagestan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当局称，枪手袭击了俄罗斯穆斯林聚居区达吉斯坦的一座教堂和一座犹太教堂，造成至少六名警察和一名东正教牧师死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/six-police-officers-and-a-priest-killed-in-russia-s-dagestan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 18:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国总理肖尔茨表示希望勒庞不会赢得法国大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/germany-s-scholz-says-he-hopes-le-pen-won-t-win-french-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨 (Olaf Scholz) 介入法国政坛，表示他希望玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 的极右翼国民联盟 (National Rally) 不会赢得法国议会选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/germany-s-scholz-says-he-hopes-le-pen-won-t-win-french-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 14:40:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨和米莱要求迅速达成欧盟-南方共同市场自由贸易协定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/scholz-milei-demand-swift-deal-on-eu-mercosur-free-trade-pact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国和阿根廷领导人呼吁欧盟与南美四个经济体迅速达成一项重大贸易协议，但遭到法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/scholz-milei-demand-swift-deal-on-eu-mercosur-free-trade-pact</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 12:42:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国左翼人士的计划包括将最高边际所得税率提高至 90%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/france-elections-2024-leftists-propose-90-top-marginal-income-tax-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果法国左翼联盟在 7 月 7 日结束的立法选举后掌权，他们将把最高边际所得税率提高至 90%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/france-elections-2024-leftists-propose-90-top-marginal-income-tax-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 10:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Engie 首席执行官称法国退出欧盟电力市场可能面临停电风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/engie-ceo-says-france-risks-blackouts-in-eu-power-market-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公用事业公司Engie SA的首席执行官表示，如果法国退出欧盟单一能源市场，该国将面临电价上涨甚至停电的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/engie-ceo-says-france-risks-blackouts-in-eu-power-market-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 10:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最新民意调查显示，法国国民阵线领先马克龙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/france-election-more-polls-show-le-pen-s-national-rally-well-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国提前举行议会选举前一周，法国国民联盟在民意调查中继续巩固领先地位，而这主要是以削弱总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙领导的中间派阵营为代价的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/france-election-more-polls-show-le-pen-s-national-rally-well-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 09:05:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡认为，随着 Gallant 访问美国，武器争端将结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/war-in-gaza-israel-s-gallant-heads-to-us-as-tensions-rise-over-arms-shipments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡重申美国推迟武器运送的说法，但他表示希望该问题能尽快得到解决，因为国防部长约阿夫加兰特将前往华盛顿进行高层会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/war-in-gaza-israel-s-gallant-heads-to-us-as-tensions-rise-over-arms-shipments</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 08:40:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>酷热天气致朝觐死亡人数升至 1,300 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-23/over-1-000-pilgrims-died-during-this-year-s-hajj-pilgrimage-in-saudi-arabia-officials-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[开罗（美联社）——沙特当局周日宣布，今年沙特阿拉伯朝觐期间，由于信徒在这个沙漠王国的伊斯兰圣地遭遇极端高温，导致 1,300 多人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-23/over-1-000-pilgrims-died-during-this-year-s-hajj-pilgrimage-in-saudi-arabia-officials-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 08:25:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰在基辅附近击落导弹 克里米亚遭受袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/war-in-ukraine-russian-kalibr-missiles-shot-down-near-kyiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国防部报告称，乌克兰对占领的克里米亚半岛实施了 ATACMS 导弹袭击，并使用集束弹药造成多人死亡和受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/war-in-ukraine-russian-kalibr-missiles-shot-down-near-kyiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 08:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
